81/zenodo.6919888" figureDoi-1="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6919892" figureDoi-2="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6919894" figureDoi-3="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6919896" figureDoi-4="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6919902" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/6919888/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/6919892/files/figure.png" httpUri-2="https://zenodo.org/record/6919894/files/figure.png" httpUri-3="https://zenodo.org/record/6919896/files/figure.png" httpUri-4="https://zenodo.org/record/6919902/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="140">Figs. 1–5</figureCitation>
